txt.en: You have caught all but the most wily of \qrats\q in Umbar Baharbêl and made safe the streets of the Free City... more or less.
Defeat many \qrats\q in Umbar Baharbêl. Not every villain and ruffian of the city names themselves sworn to the Heirs.
